entries.journal_entry_description: Track down Ral Mundi's missing shipment of starship components.
entries.journal_entry_title: Reacquire the Missing Starship Component Shipment
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Launch into space and trace the route taken by the transport that was supposed to deliver Ral's shipment. Look for anything out of the ordinary. Report back to Ral once this has been completed.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: Trace the Route Taken by the Transport
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Ral needs to know what happened in space.  Report back to him at once!
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Intimidate some Ragtags until they reveal where you might find Tomi Jinsin. Ragtags can be found all over on Corellia and often on the outskirts of most major cities, such as Coronet.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: In a last minute attempt at surrender, the last Ragtag thug you defeated blurted out that Tomi Jinsin is hiding out in a bunker near Coronet on the beach. Go there and find Tomi.
entries.task03_message_box_text: In a last minute attempt at surrender, the last Ragtag thug you defeated blurted out that Tomi Jinsin is hiding out in a bunker near Coronet on the beach. Go there and find Tomi.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Go to the Ragtag bunker and defeat Tomi Jinsin. Force him to reveal what he knows about the missing shipment.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Checking Tomi Jinsin's remains reveals a datapad with instructions to deliver the stolen shipment to the capitol building in Coronet. There's also a vague note about some smuggled spice.
entries.task05_message_box_text: Checking Tomi Jinsin's remains reveals a datapad with instructions to deliver the stolen shipment to the capitol building in Coronet. There's also a vague note about some smuggled spice.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Go to the capitol building in Coronet and look for the missing shipment inside.
entries.task06_journal_entry_title: Go Find the Shipment at the Capitol
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: The mysterious crate contains spice that was smuggled in with Ral's shipment. It's obvious Ral had no idea this was going on. The big question is: Why was this delivered to the capitol building?
entries.task07_message_box_text: The mysterious crate contains spice that was smuggled in with Ral's shipment. It's obvious Ral had no idea this was going on. The big question is: Why was this delivered to the capitol building?
entries.task08_journal_entry_description: Return to Ral at the Starport entrance and let him know you found his missing shipment.
entries.task08_journal_entry_title: Return to Ral at the Starport
entries.task09_journal_entry_description: Report to Lt. Jasper and brief him on the details of your success in finding Ral's missing shipment.
entries.task11_journal_entry_description: You have failed your task, return to Ral Mundi to let him know.
entries.task11_journal_entry_title: Return to Ral Mundi in Coronet
